==Etymology==
*Probably derived from the term [[major]], which was the military governor of a city or town during times of [[martial law]].

==Noun==
'''mayor'''

#The leader of a [[city]], sometimes as just a figurehead and sometimes as a powerful position.  They are usually elected by the [[citizen]]s of that city.
